{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A key generator that uses the HMAC based HKDF algorithm to generate a new encryption key. SHA512 is used as the hash function."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The key generation consists of two phases: extraction and expansion."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"During the extraction a pseudo random key is generated from the input key material and an optional salt."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The expansion phase uses the pseudo random key and the info data block to derive the final key."}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK"]]},"relationshipsSections":[{"kind":"relationships","identifiers":["doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/objc(cs)NSObject"],"title":"Inherits From","type":"inheritsFrom"},{"kind":"relationships","identifiers":["doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/objc(pl)NSObject","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/SBSDKStorageCryptingKeyGenerator","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/s7CVarArgP","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/s28CustomDebugStringConvertibleP","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/s23CustomStringConvertibleP","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/SQ","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/SH"],"title":"Conforms To","type":"conformsTo"}],"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/scanbotdocumentscannersdk\/sbsdkhkdfkeygenerator"]},{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/scanbotdocumentscannersdk\/sbsdkhkdfkeygenerator"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"@objcMembers","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"SBSDKHKDFKeyGenerator","kind":"identifier"}],"